<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>BABATHE.COM - 상품옵션 변경</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/library.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/common.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/templateA.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/templateB.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/templateC.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/templateD.css">
    <script src="../../js/swiper-bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="../../js/layout.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="popOpen('layerPop-goodsOptionA')">상품옵션팝업 열기</a>
    <div class="layerPop bottomUp open" id="layerPop-goodsOptionA">
        <div class="cont">
            <h1>상품 옵션을 선택/변경해 주세요.</h1>
            <div class="optionCont">
                <div class="optSelectWrap">
                    <select>
                        <option>모델명 선택</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="optSelectWrap">
                    <select>
                        <option>색상 선택</option>
                    </select>
                    <select>
                        <option>55</option>
                        <option>45</option>
                        <option>35</option>
                        <option>25</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="optSelectMessage">품절임박 : 잔여8개</div>
                <div class="placeToBtn">
                    <div class="place">
                        <span>상품 금액</span>
                        <strong>600,000원</strong>
                    </div>
                    <div class="btnWrap">
                        <button class="btn-cancel">취소</button>
                        <button class="btn-confrim">확인</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <button class="btn-close" onclick="popClose('layerPop-goodsOptionA')">팝업닫기</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>